OL,3,CGovernment promises asylum appeals
OL,4,Coverhaul as hotel protests continue
OL,6,FA new fast-track asylum appeals
OL,7,Fprocess will be introduced to speed up
OL,8,Fthe process of removing people with no
OL,9,Fright to be in the UK, Yvette Cooper
OL,10,Fhas promised, amid protests about the
OL,11,Fuse of hotel accommodation for
OL,12,Fmigrants.
OL,14,FThe Home Secretary said "completely
OL,15,Funacceptable" delays in the appeals
OL,16,Fprocess left failed asylum seekers in
OL,17,Fthe system for years.
OL,19,FThere are about 51,000 asylum appeals
OL,20,Fwaiting to be heard, taking on average
OL,21,Fmore than a year to reach a decision.
