OL,3,CGovernment promises asylum appeals
OL,4,Coverhaul as hotel protests continue
OL,6,FAs measures have been put in place to
OL,7,Fspeed up initial decisions, court
OL,8,Fdelays over appeals are now thought to
OL,9,Fbe the biggest cause of pressure in
OL,10,Fthe asylum accommodation system.
OL,12,FThe Government plans to set up a new
OL,13,Findependent panel focused on asylum
OL,14,Fappeals to help reduce the backlog, as
OL,15,Ffirst reported by the Sunday Times.
OL,17,FThe new independent body will use
OL,18,Fprofessionally-trained adjudicators,
OL,19,Frather than relying on judges.
