OL,3,CGovernment promises asylum appeals
OL,4,Coverhaul as hotel protests continue
OL,6,FMinisters are introducing a new 24-
OL,7,Fweek deadline for the first-tier
OL,8,Ftribunal to determine asylum appeals
OL,9,Fby those receiving accommodation
OL,10,Fsupport and appeals by foreign
OL,11,Foffenders.
OL,13,FBut they believe the current tribunal
OL,14,Fsystem, which covers a wide range of
OL,15,Fdifferent cases, is still failing to
OL,16,Fensure failed asylum seekers can be
OL,17,Freturned as swiftly as possible, nor
OL,18,Fcan it accommodate a fast-track system
OL,19,Ffor safe countries.
