OL,6,FShe said: "We inherited an asylum
OL,7,Fsystem in complete chaos with a
OL,8,Fsoaring backlog of asylum cases and a
OL,9,Fbroken appeals system with thousands
OL,10,Fof people in the system for years on
OL,11,Fend.
OL,13,F"That is why we are taking practical
OL,14,Fsteps to fix the foundations and
OL,15,Frestore control and order to the
OL,16,Fsystem.
OL,18,F"We are determined to substantially
OL,19,Freduce the number of people in the
OL,20,Fasylum system as part of our plan to
OL,21,Fend asylum hotels.
