OL,3,CGovernment promises asylum appeals
OL,4,Coverhaul as hotel protests continue
OL,6,FOfficial figures released earlier this
OL,7,Fmonth showed a total of 111,084 people
OL,8,Fapplied for asylum in the UK in the
OL,9,Fyear to June 2025, the highest number
OL,10,Ffor any 12-month period since current
OL,11,Frecords began in 2001.
OL,13,FThe record level of applications comes
OL,14,Fas the backlog of people waiting for
OL,15,Fan initial decision on their claims
OL,16,Fdropped to 90,812 at the end of June.
OL,18,FThere were 32,059 asylum seekers in UK
OL,19,Fhotels by the end of June. Labour has
OL,20,Fpromised to end the use of the sites
OL,21,Fby 2029.
