OL,12,Fbrought in to separate rival groups in
OL,13,Fthe Castle Park, and officers scuffled
OL,14,Fwith protesters.
OL,16,FA 37-year-old woman was arrested on
OL,17,Fsuspicion of assaulting an emergency
OL,18,Fworker.
