OL,6,FIn Horley, Surrey, about 200 anti-
OL,7,Fimmigration protesters draped in St
OL,8,FGeorge and Union flags clashed with
OL,9,Froughly 50 Stand Up to Racism
OL,10,Fprotesters.
OL,12,FThe two groups almost came together in
OL,13,Fthe early afternoon, with lines of
OL,14,Fpolice separating them.
OL,16,FThe Stand Up to Racism protesters were
OL,17,Fshepherded into a smaller area as they
OL,18,Fcontinued to chant "no hate, no fear,
OL,19,Frefugees are welcome here", which were
OL,20,Fmet with "no they're f****** not" from
OL,21,Fthe other side of the street.
