OL,7,Ftheir intention to seek legal advice
OL,8,Fas to whether they could achieve a
OL,9,Fsimilar injunction for hotels in their
OL,10,Fareas.
OL,12,FReform UK's Nigel Farage has set out
OL,13,Fplans for mass deportations if he
OL,14,Fbecomes prime minister.
